    "Traditional RNNs, however, face limitations.",
    "They tend to simply pass along all learned knowledge to the next time step without any processing.",
    "Consequently, early knowledge may be overwritten by more recent information, and long-range dependencies are challenging to capture.LSTM models introduce a gating mechanism to mitigate the vanishing gradient problem in training with long sequences.By learning word embeddings, deep learning enables the completion of natural language classification and understanding.",
    "Compared to traditional machine learning, deep learning-based NLP offers several advantages:1.",
    "Continuous learning: Deep learning continuously learns language features based on word or sentence vectorization, grasping higher-level and more abstract language features to accommodate a broad range of NLP tasks. 2."
